# wargame_rl

Reinforcement learning project that trains agents (DQN, PPO) to play tabletop wargames on a discrete grid. Agents control multiple models (units) using polar-coordinate movement to capture objectives.

**Stack**: Python 3.12+ ┬╖ UV ┬╖ Gymnasium 1.x ┬╖ PyTorch + Lightning ┬╖ Wandb ┬╖ Pydantic + pydantic-yaml ┬╖ Typer ┬╖ Loguru ┬╖ Pygame
**Tooling**: Just ┬╖ Ruff (fmt/lint, 88 cols) ┬╖ Mypy (strict) ┬╖ isort ┬╖ autoflake ┬╖ Pytest ┬╖ Pre-commit

- **Python 3.13** (UV package manager, `uv.lock`)
- **Gymnasium 1.x** тАФ RL environment (`WargameEnv`)
- **PyTorch + PyTorch Lightning** тАФ DQN and PPO training
- **Wandb** тАФ experiment tracking & video recording
- **Pydantic + pydantic-yaml** тАФ config & type models
- **Typer** тАФ CLI (`train.py`, `simulate.py`)
- **Loguru** тАФ logging
- **Pygame** тАФ human rendering

## Development Tooling

- **Just** тАФ command runner (see `Justfile`)
- **Ruff** тАФ linter & formatter (line length 88, double quotes)
- **Mypy** тАФ strict type checking (`disallow_untyped_defs`, `no_implicit_optional`)
- **isort** тАФ import sorting (Black profile)
- **autoflake** тАФ removes unused imports
- **Pytest** тАФ testing
- **Pre-commit** тАФ hooks for all of the above

## Key Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Setup | `just setup` |
| Sync deps | `just dev-sync` |
| Format | `just format` |
| Lint | `just lint` |
| Test | `just test` |
| Full validation | `just validate` |
| Train (PPO, default) | `just train <config.yaml>` |
| Train (DQN) | `just train <config.yaml> dqn` |
| Train multiple configs in parallel | `just train-multi config1.yaml config2.yaml` |
| Simulate | `just simulate-latest` |

## Project Layout

- `wargame_rl/wargame/envs/` тАФ Gymnasium environment, reward, rendering, types (see [docs/ddd-envs.md](docs/ddd-envs.md) for DDD structure and extension)
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/dqn/` тАФ DQN agent, Lightning module, replay buffer, config
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/ppo/` тАФ PPO actor-critic, Lightning module, agent, config
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/common/` тАФ Shared: factory, observation, dataset, device, wandb, callbacks
- `wargame_rl/wargame/model/net.py` тАФ RL_Network base, MLPNetwork, TransformerNetwork
- `wargame_rl/wargame/types.py` тАФ `Experience` / `ExperienceBatch`
- `examples/env_config/` тАФ YAML env configs
- `tests/` тАФ Pytest suite, fixtures in `conftest.py`
- `docs/` тАФ design docs (DDD in envs: `docs/ddd-envs.md`)
- `train.py` / `simulate.py` / `main.py` тАФ entry points
